- **Regulatory Requirements:** Common law, contract law
- **AI Restrictions:** Prohibited from all external AI; extreme caution with internal AI
{% elif dtype == "Customer Data (purchase history, preferences)" %}
- **Default Classification:** Confidential
- **Regulatory Requirements:** Privacy Act 1988, APPs, consumer data rights
- **AI Restrictions:** Anonymise before processing; purpose limitation applies
{% elif dtype == "Employee Data (HR records, performance)" %}
- **Default Classification:** Confidential
- **Regulatory Requirements:** Privacy Act 1988, Fair Work Act
- **AI Restrictions:** HR approval required; anonymise for analytics
{% elif dtype == "Publicly Available Data" %}
- **Default Classification:** Public
- **Regulatory Requirements:** Copyright Act
- **AI Restrictions:** Verify source and accuracy of AI outputs
{% elif dtype == "Biometric Data" %}
- **Default Classification:** Restricted
- **Regulatory Requirements:** Privacy Act 1988 (sensitive information)
- **AI Restrictions:** Prohibited from all external AI tools
{% elif dtype == "Children's Data (under 18)" %}
- **Default Classification:** Restricted
- **Regulatory Requirements:** Privacy Act 1988, UN Convention on the Rights of the Child, Online Safety Act 2021
- **AI Restrictions:** Prohibited from external AI; internal use requires PIA and parental consent; see Section 4B
{% elif dtype == "AI-Inferred Data (profiles, predictions)" %}
- **Default Classification:** Confidential
- **Regulatory Requirements:** Privacy Act 1988 (APPs 3, 6, 13), POLA Act 2024 (automated decision transparency)
- **AI Restrictions:** Must be explainable; individuals have right to request explanation of inferences; retention limits apply
{% endif %}

